${color}${GOTO 40}Freq${GOTO 94}${color1}${freq_g}GHz${GOTO 224}${color}Total Cores${alignr 46}${color1}${execi 65000 cat /proc/cpuinfo | grep "model name" | wc -l}
# CPU graph
${voffset -2}${GOTO 40}${color}${cpugraph 24,278 EAE3D0 DD3A21 -t}
# Core temperature
